text: Ancita ochraceovittata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1936. It is indigenous to Papua New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Ancita ochraceovittata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ancita Category:Beetles described in 1936
title: Ancita ochraceovittata
